{"tid":670822,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日拉麵(一幻同周月)","createTime":"2018-05-19T16:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T05:56:39.000Z","uid":138155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87ce27c020cac2866886e2729eb7ac66503b14bd","tid":670822,"uid":138155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/002414_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F002414_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=1b3cad58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/002419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F002419_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c8efeff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/20/002425_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F20%2F002425_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cb10b68a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前睇中出兄嗰post，話一幻喺香港嘅分店唔係咁掂，但係見今日都得閑就走去試下...結果都係去食一次就夠喇，再去就不了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完一幻試埋周月喺銅鑼灣新開嗰間分店，銅鑼灣嗰間嘅質素明顯同上環總店有差距，都係唔洗再去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e935ccd0bbcc17825bee51da6cf4288c8a4298","tid":670822,"uid":178110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fd686b2f0bdbf95bc99732b5d1568782d1bf692","tid":670822,"uid":36432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:47:30.000Z","msg":"上環周月<img src=\"/asse